Dear <%=@note.student.counselor.first_name%>,
<%=@note.counselor.first_name %> <%=@note.counselor.last_name %> has posted a note on one of your students, 
<%=@note.student.first_name %> <%=@note.student.last_name %>, and has wished to notify you.

Note Details:
===================================================================
Student: 		<%=@note.student.first_name %> <%=@note.student.last_name %>
Note Author:	<%=@note.counselor.first_name %> <%=@note.counselor.last_name %>
Summary:		<%=@note.summary%>
Date:			<%=@note.created_at.strftime('%m/%d/%Y %I:%M %p') %>
Category:		<%=@note.category.name%>
Tags:			<%- @note.tags.each do |tag| %> <%=tag.name + ((tag != @note.tags.last) ? ',' : '')%> <% end %>
Notes:
<%=@note.notes%>




